themes: collaborative partnership between city, artists/organizations, and citizens
community engagement as a core value
support structures for artists and organizations (admin, training, skill-ups)
key_phrases: City 1-provides funds, 2-supports (admin, training, skill-ups), 3-engages the Community
Artist/Org 1-applies for funding, 2-creates Art, 3-engages the Community
Citizens 1-attend Art, 2-support (money, time, talent), 3-engage with others in Community (share experiences)
solutions_proposed: Adopt a 3-pronged partnership approach involving city, artists/organizations, and citizens
City should provide funds, administrative support, training, skill-ups, and community engagement
Artists/organizations should apply for funding, create art, and engage the community
Citizens should attend art, support with money, time, and talent, and engage with others by sharing experiences
